Package io.github.eutro.wasm2j.ssa

Class IRBuilder

java.lang.Object
io.github.eutro.wasm2j.ssa.IRBuilder
public class IRBuilder extends Object
An IR, or instruction, builder, which encapsulates a position in a function where instructions are being inserted.
